BEGIN_TEXT
Write the sum using sigma notation:
$BR$BR
\( $c[1]+$c[2]+$c[3]+$c[4]+\cdots+$f =\sum_{n=1}^{A} B \).  Then
$BR$BR
\(A=\) \{ans_rule(15) \}
$BR$BR
\(B=\) \{ans_rule(15) \}
END_TEXT

ANS(num_cmp($a));
ANS(fun_cmp("$b*n",vars=>['n']));

